- **Ownership** â€” every `Book` has a `user_id`; the list query filters by `current_user.id`, and update/delete go through `_owned_book_or_404`, which returns **403** if you don't own the book and **404** if it doesn't exist. Users can only see and touch their own list.
- **Books** â€” title, author, `status` (`to-read` / `reading` / `finished`), optional `rating` (1â€“5). You can add, change status/rating inline, delete, and filter by status. Status/rating inputs are validated server-side against the allowed set.
- **Storage** â€” SQLite at `reading_list.db`, auto-created on first run via `db.create_all()`.
- **Port** â€” `app.run(..., port=5034)`.

